metadata.name: SWEED GA-ME NFT
metadata.description: A vinyl figure concept collections of 7,777 consisting of multiple GA-ME (gummie) bears NFTs brought to life within this every growing metaverse and Web 3.0 space. Ultimately, Sweed not only develop a streetwear brand but also brings out unique storytelling and childhood memories. All our unique NFTs come with their own colour way RED, YELLOW, GREEN . Each possess special abilities and utilities required to live and thrive within the virtual blockchain space.
